data.description: SELLER WILL PAY up to $10,000 for BUYER CLOSING COSTS or INTEREST RATE BUY-DOWN!! ENJOY COUNTRY LIVING at its BEST in this REMODELED & UPDATED 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home set on 1.448 ACRES in OAK VALLEY. IMAGINE relaxing on the rockers or dining al fresco on your large SCREENED-IN PORCH. And, you will love the SPACIOUS KITCHEN with CUSTOM CABINETRY & a HUGE CENTER ISLAND as well as a coffee bar! The PRIMARY BEDROOM boasts a WALK-IN CEDAR CLOSET as well as ALL NEW BATH FIXTURES & is split from the other 2 bedrooms & second remodeled bath. And, the FAMILY ROOM provides lots of extra space for entertaining, hobbies or simply relaxing. An ELECTRONIC GATE leads to the fenced acreage which provides room for gardening... for flowers, fruits, vegetables & grape trellises...and MANY EXTRAS all ready for your country lifestyle such as a LARGE 15x24 WORKSHOP, equipment shed, & chicken coops, too! BE SURE TO SCHEDULE YOUR PRIVATE TOUR SOON!!
